{"tid":275740,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"求教！比教車師父撚化定點？","createTime":"2017-06-08T09:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T06:45:19.000Z","uid":33866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51fb9d8f528c55c698469fff4e0cf4a051b823a3","tid":275740,"uid":33866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"小弟9月中考車 ， 岩岩想約教車師父第一堂時間 <br />\n<br />\n佢就話8月中先學都未遲， 話我買左15堂（每堂45分鐘） ， 8月中開始同我每星期上2-4堂 ， 一個月搞掂佢 <br />\n<br />\n想問咁玩法會唔會太大風險定反而更好？"},{"pid":"5ea6eebd7bce878391e909bede375072ff9943b6","tid":275740,"uid":31705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:27:11.000Z","msg":"其實早學冇用 你愈早學就愈快用哂d堂補鐘 如果你真係試左幾堂真係覺得自己冇天份味臨考前一兩星期補堂學未遲"},{"pid":"724c09f853a859176c7d95f15de4b59e76946377","tid":275740,"uid":84954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"佢無水你<br />\n你15堂,45分鐘一堂<br />\n通常2堂(個半鐘)咁上<br />\n即係有7次<br />\n但最後1次通常約考之前<br />\n用黎熱身再考<br />\n剩返嗰1堂(45分鐘)<br />\n就係計租佢車黎考試"},{"pid":"7a5e8562de69acdd1a93d304bca5bedff5ebddd9","tid":275740,"uid":14557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:38:24.000Z","msg":"佢啱 唔係你上兩堂 隔一排又唔記得"},{"pid":"2a4f10a2a161090e780a19dfa27ff34b9e6f1581","tid":275740,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:41:16.000Z","msg":"買隻車game搞店啦"},{"pid":"d5278ec6d63f5cf8144ae8a97ef7138ef934b067","tid":275740,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8102f6a50d3825cf8ca575fa2a3f2c8cfd453043","tid":275740,"uid":73123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:44:40.000Z","msg":"早幾年我上左成3x個鐘，除番開咪即係樓主嘅4x堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無俾師父水到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdeb6a0593d65d52a4c73f99f11506937970bd0","tid":275740,"uid":33826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20